{"time":"2026-05-02T12:57:12.471Z","category":"agent_end","message":"agent_end","data":{"finalMessage":"","success":true,"event":{"messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-05-02 12:56 UTC] 给出五一假期热点"}],"timestamp":1777726605177},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要了解五一假期的热点信息。这是一个信息查询类请求，我需要搜索五一假期相关的热点新闻和资讯。\n\n让我使用 web_search 技能来搜索相关信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sm1qifluhpv7_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":33990,"output":74,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34064,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777726605194,"responseId":"chatcmpl-37ca7a44-1542-44aa-93df-e9d6e988d4f5"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sm1qifluhpv7_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with structured results. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，返回结构化搜索结果。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777726612924},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要用 miaoda-studio-cli search-summary 来搜索五一假期热点信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_he5hotwmue53_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"2025五一假期热点新闻\" --output json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":532,"output":63,"cacheRead":34043,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34638,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777726612939,"responseId":"chatcmpl-05f6bb49-4023-4007-bfff-5cec43fe7246"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_he5hotwmue53_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"堵山堵海堵桥堵路!五一 3 亿人次出行创高峰_民生领域博主\",\n      \"url\": \"http://m.toutiao.com/group/7635189589329691146/\",\n      \"site_name\": \"\",\n      \"publish_time\": \"\",\n      \"summary\": \"2025 年五一假期，全国迎来 “全民出游” 热潮，堵山、堵海、堵桥、堵路成为普遍景象。文旅部数据显示，5 天假期国内出游达3.14 亿人次，同比增长 6.4%;旅游总花费1802.69 亿元，同比增长 8%。从山岳景区到滨海沙滩，从高速路网到城市桥梁，客流车流双双 “爆表”，...\\n\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"人气旺 市面暖 活力足——2025年“五一”假