├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777726612924},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要用 miaoda-studio-cli search-summary 来搜索五一假期热点信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"callfunctionhe5hotwmue531","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"2025五一假期热点新闻\" --output json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":532,"output":63,"cacheRead":34043,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34638,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777726612939,"responseId":"chatcmpl-05f6bb49-4023-4007-bfff-5cec43fe7246"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"callfunctionhe5hotwmue531","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"堵山堵海堵桥堵路!五一 3 亿人次出行创高峰_民生领域博主\",\n      \"url\": \"http://m.toutiao.com/group/7635189589329691146/\",\n      \"site_name\": \"\",\n      \"publish_time\": \"\",\n      \"summary\": \"2025 年五一假期，全国迎来 “全民出游” 热潮，堵山、堵海、堵桥、堵路成为普遍景象。文旅部数据显示，5 天假期国内出游达3.14 亿人次，同比增长 6.4%;旅游总花费1802.69 亿元，同比增长 8%。从山岳景区到滨海沙滩，从高速路网到城市桥梁，客流车流双双 “爆表”，...\\n\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"人气旺 市面暖 活力足——2025年“五一”假期盘点__中国政府网\"