n] 范围内的好数字是：2, 5, 6, 9\n- 1 → 1（相同，不是好数字）\n- 2 → 5（不同，是好数字）\n- 3 → 无效\n- 4 → 无效\n- 5 → 2（不同，是好数字）\n- 6 → 9（不同，是好数字）\n- 7 → 无效\n- 8 → 8（相同，不是好数字）\n- 9 → 6（不同，是好数字）\n- 10 → 10（包含无效数字4，不是好数字）\n```\n\n---\n\n### 💡 解题思路\n\n1. **遍历**：对 1 到 n 的每个数字检查\n2. **有效性判断**：如果包含 3、4、7 任意一个 → 不是好数字\n3. **变化性判断**：如果不包含 2、5、6、9 任意一个（只有 0、1、8）→ 旋转后相同，不是好数字\n4. **同时满足以上两条** → 是好数字\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 核心代码（Python）\n\n```python\nclass Solution:\n    def rotatedDigits(self, n: int) -> int:\n        invalid = {'3', '4', '7'}\n        change = {'2', '5', '6', '9'}\n        same = {'0', '1', '8'}\n        \n        count = 0\n        for i in range(1, n + 1):\n            s = str(i)\n            # 包含无效数字\n            if any(c in invalid for c in s):\n                continue\n            # 包含变化数字\n            if any(c in change for c in s):\n                count += 1\n        return count\n```\n\n---\n\n要去挑战一下吗 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":2654,"output":696,"cacheRead":87803,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91153,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777727086061,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2afc1ad6-d1c1-424f-a0d4-deb5b42112f7"}],"success":true,"durationMs":304282}}}
